    <p>Stu­dents will not be al­lowed to sit the ex­ams if they are:</p>
    <p>A con­firmed case of Covid-19 in­fec­tion</p>
    <p>On quar­an­tine or­der</p>
    <p>On stay-home no­tice (ex­cept those who have trav­elled over­seas due to com­pas­sion­ate rea­sons)</p>
    <p>On leave of ab­sence due to close con­tact with a Covid-19 con­firmed case</p>
    <p>Stu­dents will be al­lowed to sit the ex­ams if they:</p>
    <p>Test neg­a­tive for Covid-19 and are on leave of ab­sence as a re­sult of stay­ing in the same house­hold with in­di­vid­u­als on home quar­an­tine or­der</p>
    <p>Are on med­i­cal leave due to acute res­pi­ra­tory in­fec­tion but test neg­a­tive for Covid-19</p>
    <p>Are on ap­proved ab­sence as a re­sult of stay­ing in the same house­hold with adults (aged 18 and above) who have flu-like symp­toms</p>


